Write a function createEvenArray that takes a non-negative integer n as an argument and returns an array containing n even numbers.

Example:

createEvenArray (5) return [0, 2, 4, 6, 8];
createEvenArray (2) return [0, 2];
createEvenArray (1) return [0];
createEvenArray (0) return []

Solution:

function createEvenArray(n){
  let arr = [];
  for(let i = 0; i < n * 2; i++) {
    if (i % 2 === 0) arr.push(i);
  }
  return arr;
}
